Description: Provides datasets and an interactive Shiny dashboard for exploring
    bushfire patterns in southeastern Australia from 1997 to 2018. The package
    combines Fire Weather Index (FWI) data with satellite-derived burned area
    records to visualize long-term climateâ€“fire relationships, summarize yearly
    statistics, and calculate correlations between weather and fire intensity.
